Prompt Manager

Electron desktop app for building AI prompts from:
- Instructions
- Backend / website code
- Android app code

Run:
1. npm install
2. npm start

Key behavior:
- Add files, folders, or subfolders to Backend / Website and Android sections.
- Saved prompts keep source paths, so reopening a prompt reloads the latest files from disk.
- If a selected source is inside a Git repository, use Pull Git to run git pull before rebuilding the prompt.
- Prompt exports are written to your Documents\PromptManager folder.
